  <text>
     <body>
     <div type="poem" subtype="to_the__reader">
   <pb facs="8"/>
   <head>
      <hi>Tho. Lee,</hi> to the Reader.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>IF thou desire thy God to looue,</l>
      <l>And would the causes vnderstand:</l>
      <l>It shall be good for thy behooue,</l>
      <l>This little Booke to take in hand,</l>
      <l>The way to heauen it will thée teach,</l>
      <l>And how to shun the paines of hell:</l>
      <l>It to thy soule, pure thinges dooth preach,</l>
      <l>Peruse, and immitate it well.</l>
      <closer>
         <signed>Tho. Lee.</signed>
      </closer>
   </lg>
   <trailer>FINIS.</trailer>
</div>
